---
import { Anchor } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about-section" class="py-0 bg-swiss-bg border-b border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 border-x border-gray-200 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-0">
    
    <!-- Left Column: Manifesto -->
    <div class="p-12 md:p-24 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-200">
      <div class="mb-8">
         <Anchor className="w-12 h-12 text-primary" strokeWidth={1.5} />
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-swiss-text mb-8 tracking-tighter">BİZ KİMİZ?</h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-swiss-text/90 leading-relaxed font-medium">
        "Düşünce ve Kitap Topluluğu, entelektüel üretimin tüketimden daha değerli olduğuna inananların limanıdır. 
        Amacımız, fikirlerin çarpıştığı ama asla incitmediği, derinliğin sığlığa galip geldiği bir alan yaratmaktır."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Stats Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="p-12 border-b border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col justify-center">
         <span class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-primary mb-2 tracking-tighter">5K+</span>
         <span class="text-sm uppercase font-bold text-swiss-muted tracking-wide">Aktif Üye</span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-12 border-b border-gray-200 flex flex-col justify-center">
         <span class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-secondary mb-2 tracking-tighter">120+</span>
         <span class="text-sm uppercase font-bold text-swiss-muted tracking-wide">Atölye</span>
      </div>
       <div class="p-12 border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col justify-center">
         <span class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-swiss-text mb-2 tracking-tighter">850+</span>
         <span class="text-sm uppercase font-bold text-swiss-muted tracking-wide">Kitap Analizi</span>
      </div>
       <div class="p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
         <span class="block text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-swiss-text mb-2 tracking-tighter">∞</span>
         <span class="text-sm uppercase font-bold text-swiss-muted tracking-wide">Fikir</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
